y el bombardino a mucho público que sorprendido descubrió nuestros instrumentos.<br /><br />Al finalizar, los más pequeños pudieron descubrir los fácil que es tocar un bombardino.&nbsp; <br /><br />Aquí os dejo algunas fotos de nuestra actuación.<br /><br />Fotos cortesía de: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/fotosdeaj" target="_blank">Antonio Jiménez García</a> <br /><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-K-_RafQOmX8/WSApZFNEPpI/AAAAAAAADAg/9GKAOBn0mU4ahQOYKJdO5oXDdtpsUr94gCLcB/s1600/Calzada8.jpeg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="251" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-K-_RafQOmX8/WSApZFNEPpI/AAAAAAAADAg/9GKAOBn0mU4ahQOYKJdO5oXDdtpsUr94gCLcB/s400/Calzada8.jpeg" width="400" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ojqd3UaZcuQ/WSApZYx-B_I/AAAAAAAADAk/Z5o8bPVtghMOT2iaVx2hBBcqeS6TbBv2wCLcB/s1600/Calzada9.jpeg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="251" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ojqd3UaZcuQ/WSApZYx-B_I/AAAAAAAADAk/Z5o8bPVtghMOT2iaVx2hBBcqeS6TbBv2wCLcB/s400/Calzada9.jpeg" width="400" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-KsBaOz01jWw/WSApXNUgKJI/AAAAAAAADAE/FP3ief7gt2kxquxhDTVtcs5EHvgiu4k6ACLcB/s1600/Calzada11.jpeg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="400" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-KsBaOz01jWw/WSApXNUgKJI/AAAAAAAADAE/FP3ief7gt2kxquxhDTVtcs5EHvgiu4k6ACLcB/s400/Calzada11.jpeg" width="251" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-kFZEDVltWmY/WSApWjG_FqI/AAAAAAAAC_8/apY5VMmDv-ElciKQV1FHyYaEq3kGMqEdgCLcB/s1600/Calzada12.jpeg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="251" src="https:/